---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Learn more about mindfulwrld and our mission to promote mindfulness and intentional living."
>
  <section class="about-page">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-content">
        <h1>About mindfulwrld</h1>

        <div class="prose">
          <p>
            Welcome to mindfulwrld, your companion on the journey to a more mindful,
            intentional life.
          </p>

          <h2>Our Mission</h2>
          <p>
            We believe that mindfulness is the key to living a more fulfilling,
            present, and joyful life. Through our blog, we share insights, tips,
            and inspiration to help you cultivate mindfulness in your daily routine.
          </p>

          <h2>What We Write About</h2>
          <p>
            Our content covers a wide range of topics related to mindfulness and
            wellness, including:
          </p>

          <ul>
            <li>Meditation techniques and practices</li>
            <li>Mindful living tips for everyday life</li>
            <li>Mental health and emotional wellness</li>
            <li>Self-care and personal growth</li>
            <li>Stress management and relaxation</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Join Our Community</h2>
          <p>
            Whether you're new to mindfulness or have been practicing for years,
            we're here to support you on your journey. Explore our blog posts,
            try our techniques, and discover what works best for you.
          </p>

          <p>
            Thank you for being part of the mindfulwrld community. Together,
            let's create a more mindful world.
          </p>

          <div class="cta">
            <a href="/blog" class="btn btn-primary">Read Our Blog</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    padding: var(--space-16) 0;
    min-height: 60vh;
  }

  .about-content {
    max-width: var(--max-width-prose);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-content h1 {
    font-size: var(--font-size-5xl);
    color: var(--color-black);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta {
    margin-top: var(--space-12);
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-page {
      padding: var(--space-12) 0;
    }

    .about-content h1 {
      font-size: var(--font-size-3xl);
    }
  }
</style>
